# Google Sheet Apps Script Web App URL for subscription syncing
# Steps to set this up:
# 1. In Google Sheets (linked to your Google Form), go to Extensions -> Apps Script
# 2. Paste the provided doGet/doPost Apps Script
# 3. Deploy as "Web App" with Access set to "Anyone"
# 4. Copy the resulting Macro Exec URL and save it as this environment variable
GOOGLE_SHEET_WEBAPP_URL=
